r />\n換算完做數字再做加減<br />\n做完加減再換算<br />\n<br />\n思路就係咁。之後既野自己諗。"},{"pid":"c5b3eaaa618f02634e6f7288a296956cd616d9ed","tid":410433,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"可以,好簡單,見過有人問"},{"pid":"e0b38b4ce4ac4d46680a95cbd56c5d954d1543f7","tid":410433,"uid":41583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡易換算問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你工時為9-18<br />\n<br />\n星期一既10點等於1。等於(一-1)x9+(10-9)<br />\n<br />\n星期三既14點等於23。等於(三-1)x9+(14-9)<br />\n<br />\n換算完做數字再做加減<br />\n做完加減再換算<br />\n<br />\n思路就係咁。之後既野自己諗。</blockquote><br />\n唔明呀，點解要（一-1）最後等於1姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a434e8ee1e5f141287198b07f26823b1fd0143b","tid":410433,"uid":41583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:26:58.000Z","msg":"負評啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786ecac9baec2c9d4be1c3c391e256f1a50c5b73","tid":410433,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>簡易換算問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你工時為9-18<br />\n<br />\n星期一既10點等於1。等於(一-1)x9+(10-9)<br />\n<br />\n星期三既14點等於23。等於(三-1)x9+(14-9)<br />\n<br />\n換算完做數字再做加減<br />\n做完加減再換算<br />\n<br />\n思路就係咁。之後既野自己諗。</blockquote><br />\n唔明呀，點解要（一-1）最後等於1姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>不如你講下你到底用咩工具自動化成件事"},{"pid":"9d39d517e19e6f733e585ca371b4e84ad93e49b0","tid":410433,"uid":96965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:54:51.000Z","msg":"講多無謂<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b93b76ceba7160fa2cd963588427989b3cbfb67","tid":410433,"uid":41583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>簡易換算問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你工時為9-18<br />\n<br />\n星期一既10點等於1。等於(一-1)x9+(10-9)<br />\n<br />\n星期三既14點等於23。等於(三-1)x9+(14-9)<br />\n<br />\n換算完做數字再做加減<br />\n做完加減再換算<br />\n<br />\n思路就係咁。之後既野自己諗。</blockquote><br />\n唔明呀，點解要（一-1）最後等於1姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>不如你講下你到底用咩工具自動化成件事</blockquote><br />\n就係想問會唔會可以可以入條程式入計數機，<br />\n然後自動化成件事<br />\n或者excel個啲都得<br />\n就咁計唔係計唔到，係計得慢"},{"pid":"4326a2256a2dca5c9afb1dfc07a7354235d59fd5","tid":410433,"uid":102271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"都幾複雜 你個output要係幾號<br />\n即係要有埋個月份有幾多日既information<br />\n仲有如果你剩係input日期 仲要加多條式check個日期係星期幾"},{"pid":"1aebc3f65b1d22d72913566faa863d172d7c9adb","tid":410433,"uid":102271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都幾複雜 你個output要係幾號<br />\n即係要有埋個月份有幾多日既information<br />\n仲有如果你剩係input日期 仲要加多條式check個日期係星期幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申 programing初學者"},{"pid":"1812130cdf55b0c7ea54afd371dfcae21761cb1b","tid":410433,"uid":41583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都幾複雜 你個output要係幾號<br />\n即係要有埋個月份有幾多日既information<br />\n仲有如果你剩係input日期 仲要加多條式check個日期係星期幾</blockquote><br />\n咁應該都係自己計快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026de0c0bd9b02d2b76f8ab2e8729b05647ae07c","tid":410433,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"要detect香港公眾假期, <br />\n邊個肯定期update呢啲資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adce6f311b63be8f883dc1225e77aa3c6d2e5479","tid":410433,"uid":64740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我要係人地工作時間16個小時前交稿<br />\n而星期一至五工作時間為9小時，<br />\n星期六為4小時，星期日同公眾假期唔計<br />\n例如而家係22號10點，<br />\n16小時前交係20號12點<br />\n我想每次快啲計完<br />\n會唔會可以出條程式放入計數機方便計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽日試下幫你<img src=\"/